  "content": {
    "prompt": "Construct a program that performs increment/decrement operations on variable a (with initial value of 4) and variable b (with initial value of 5) and prints the following output as the result of these operations:\\n-1\\n3",
    "source_code": "public class JDecInc1 {\n\tpublic static void main(String[] args) {\n\t\t//Step 1: Define the variables\n\t\tint a = 4; \n\t\tint b = 5;\n\t\t//Step 2: Perform the operations and print the first output\n\t\tSystem.out.println( a++ - b-- ); \n\t\t//Step 3: Perform the operations and print the second output\n\t\tSystem.out.println( ++a - --b ); \n\t}\n}"
  },
